{"tid":399262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得而家個人生好悶","createTime":"2017-09-13T20:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T22:52:21.000Z","uid":88875,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e2b2aac5dc9c6228e44e8bca9b0235bf4c2bac","tid":399262,"uid":88875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T20:48:27.000Z","msg":"本身份人做好多野都會有悶既一日 有日打打下機覺得而家呢個人生都幾悶想死左佢再黎過 我自已第二下反應都嚇一跳估唔到自已會咁諗 所以想知有冇人都咁諗過<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔係負面 唔係咩壓力大睇唔開或者逃避咩 係純粹想知有冇人試過咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8b74708e2bc9188005620ffab5355dec3603ba","tid":399262,"uid":146924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T22:52:21.000Z","msg":"先唔好講話死咗仲有冇得再投胎呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾你投多次胎下一世分分鐘仲悶過你而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}